        {
            "name": "Charau-ka Butcher",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [],
            "text": "While charau-kas are well known for their brutality, some frighten even others of their kind with their obsession with violence.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Humanoid</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"14\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Society</a></u>)</b>: DC 22",
